Tech
Frontend: React, TailwindCSS, Chart.js
Backend: Node.js, Express
Database: SQLite
Payments: Stripe API (test mode)

FEATURES

1. Product List
Stored in SQLite or backup to products.json in frontend
Use placeholder images and descriptions
2. Cart Functionality
Add, remove, update quantity
Local state or Context API
3. Stripe Checkout
Use Stripe test keys
Simple checkout flow - Stripe-hosted payment page
4. Admin Dashboard (Mockup)
Basic Chart.js bar/line chart (hardcoded stats or SQLite analytics)

